titles.title: Dismissing the election contest against Jay Dickey.

action.text: The House Committee on House Administration reported an original measure, H. Rept. 103-109, by Mr. Kleczka.

calendar.text: Placed on the House Calendar, Calendar No. 44.

action.text: DEBATE - The House proceeded with one hour of debate.
The previous question was ordered without objection.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to by voice vote.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 5/25/1993--Introduced. Dismisses the Fourth Congressional District of Arkansas election contest of Bill McCuen, contestant, against Jay Dickey, contestee.
